<button class="accordion">What are the four types of business writing?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>The four types of business writing:</p>
<li>Instructional business writing.</li>
<li>Informational business writing.</li>
<li>Persuasive business writing.</li>
<li>Transactional business writing.</li>
