<button class="accordion">What is a report in informational business writing?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Perhaps the bulk of informational writing is report writing. Organisations rely on reports to act, to communicate business and technical information, to capture work completed, to record incidents, to finalise projects and recommendations, and to act as an archive. A well-written report allows the reader to grasp the content quickly and, if applicable, make informed decisions.</p>
