<button class="accordion">What is a minute in informational business writing?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>A summary of the proceedings of a meeting. A record of discussions, decisions, and assignments for attendees and others.</p>
</div>
<button class="accordion">What is persuasive business writing?</button>
